      • parse

        public static Date parse(String dateString)

        Parse the provided date.

        The date string can be in any of the following formats:
        • timestamp in milliseconds
        • yyyy/MM
        • yyyy/MM/dd
        • yyyy/MM/dd HH
        • yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm
        • yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss
        • yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss.SSS
        You can use a space, '-', '/', '_', ':', '|', or '.' to separate the parts.
        Parameters:
        dateString - The date string to parse
        Returns:
        parsed date

      • parseTime

        public static Long parseTime(String dateString)

        Parse the provided date and returns the time in milliseconds.

        The date string can be in any of the following formats:
        • timestamp in milliseconds
        • yyyy/MM
        • yyyy/MM/dd
        • yyyy/MM/dd HH
        • yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm
        • yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss
        • yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss.SSS
        You can use a space, '-', '/', '_', ':', '|', or '.' to separate the parts.
        Parameters:
        dateString - The date string to parse
        Returns:
        parsed date
